I went to visit @drdonovansmolich last week for a chiropractic session and it was a rejuvenating experience! Dr. Donovan helped me relieve tension in my back and neck and he gave me insightful information about different healing methods.

For those of you who don’t know, I got in a serious car crash in April 2022 that I am still recovering from. Not only were the physical injuries detrimental to my body, but the mental trauma I suffered was almost unbearable. I became extremely depressed to the point where I could barely eat and I lost 15 pounds. Losing so much weight caused me to struggle with body image issues and I had to take a step back from modeling. It was one of the darkest times in my life, but I like to think that everything happens for a reason. You have to experience the lows to appreciate the highs, and now I’m stronger than ever physically and mentally.

If you’ve been searching for a chiropractor, I highly recommended Dr. Donovan. He truly cares about his patients and he is extremely knowledgeable about all things mind and body. You can also mention my name for a discount!
